    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="witness" subtype="poem"  met="-+|-+|-+|-+" rhyme="aa">
                <head type="title"><handShift new="#HANDJJR" script="cursive" medium="ink"/>The Rhine<ref type="gloss_textual" target="the_rhine_poem_glosses_textual.php#HANDGLOSS" /><ref type="gloss_contextual" target="the_rhine_glosses_contextual.php#THERHINETITLE"/></head>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>We saw it where its billow swells</l>
                    <l>Beneath the ridge of <placeName corresp="#DRACHENFELS">Drachenfells</placeName><ref type="gloss_contextual" target="the_rhine_glosses_contextual.php#DRACHENFELS"/></l>
                    <l>We saw it where its ripples ride</l>
                    <l>Neath <geogName corresp="#EHRENBREITSTEIN">Ehrenbreitstein</geogName>&#x02BC;s beetling pride</l>
                    <l>We saw it where its whirlpools roar</l>
                    <l>Among the rocks of gaunt <placeName corresp="#STGOAR">St Goar</placeName></l> 
                    <l>In all its aspect is as fair</l>
                    <l>That aspect changes everywhere</l>
                    <l>From <geogName corresp="#RHAETIANALPS">Rhetian</geogName> and <geogName corresp="#DINARICALPS">Dinaric</geogName> crest<ref type="gloss_contextual" target="the_rhine_glosses_contextual.php#DINARIC"/></l>
                    <l>Foam the <del rend="strikethrough">wild</del> wild waters to the west<ref type="gloss_textual" target="the_rhine_poem_glosses_textual.php#FOAMGLOSS" /></l>
                    <l>From fearful <placeName corresp="#SPLUGEN">Splugen</placeName>s glaciered head</l> 
                    <l>The mighty torrent dashes dread</l><pb/>
                    <l>And swelled by every Alpine snow</l>
                    <l>Now see it chase these clffs below</l>
                    <l>On whose high summits deeply rent</l>
                    <l>Rise many a fortress battlement</l>
                    <l>Seeming the lords of rock &#x0026; hill</l> 
                    <l>And mighty in their ruin still.</l>
                </lg>
            </div>
            <div type="date">
